<title>Preface</title>


<para>

The Rocks Condor Roll uses the latest stable Condor Release
to provide High Throughput Computing environment for Rocks clusters.  
The Rocks Condor Roll builds on the very good work by the Condor team, 
to seamlessly install the <emphasis>de facto</emphasis> standard grid 
middleware on Rocks Clusters.

</para>


<para>

Please visit the <ulink url="http://www.cs.wisc.edu/condor/">Condor
Project Homepage</ulink> to learn more about Condor and the 
software releases.

</para>

</preface>
